videos.description: Ray Spalding shows off his athleticism with two high-flying alley-oop dunks giving Louisville the early lead over Middle Tennessee.
videos.headline: Louisville showing off early with two alley-oops

videos.description: Anas Mahmoud runs the floor after the steal and cleans up the missed 3-pointer with a putback slam.
videos.headline: Louisville shows off hustle with steal, putback dunk

videos.description: Donovan Sims throws the beautiful lob to Brandon Walters who finishes the slam.
videos.headline: Middle Tennessee connects on alley-oop
